Instructions for installing SFML library to Linux

//Install the library
sudo apt-get install libsfml-dev
*other OS install library instructions at https://www.sfml-dev.org/tutorials/2.5/

//Need to compile in this order on terminal
1)
g++ -c audiomain.cpp audio.cpp

2)
g++ audiomain.o audio.o -o minimusic -lsfml-graphics -lsfml-window -lsfml-system -lsfml-audio

3)
./minimusic

Note: The companion music files and image are located inside folder "audiofiles", which is included in the same directory inside the repository. 
Thank you for playing, literally!
